  <lyrics>[V1]
 /Kay pacha kawsaypi tukuy runas
 Mask’anku mana kajta./
 /Diospa j atún munakuyninta
 Qhesachashallanku./
 
[V2]
 /Munasqa hermano, kallpachakuy,
 Supay atipanapaj./
 /Jap'ikuy Señor Jesusmanta,
 Pay yanapasonqa./
 
[V3]
 /Diospa Palabranta willaypuni
 Tukuynejpi runasman./
 /Janaj pachapi Cristo Jesús
 Pilluta qosonqa./
 
</lyrics></song>